<topic id="xslt-quick-assist">
  <title>XSLT Quick Assist Support</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Editing XSL Stylesheets<indexterm>quick assist support</indexterm></indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Quick Assist</uicontrol> support helps you to rapidly access search and
      refactoring actions. If one or more actions are available in the current context, they are
      accessible via a yellow bulb help marker placed on the cursor line, in the editor line number
      stripe. Also, you can invoke the <uicontrol>Quick Assist</uicontrol> menu if you press <b
        product="developer editor">Alt + 1</b><b product="developerEclipse editorEclipse">Ctrl +
        1</b> keys (<b product="developer editor">Meta + Alt + 1</b><b
        product="developerEclipse editorEclipse">Meta 1</b> on Mac OS X) on your keyboard.</p>
    <p>Two categories of actions are available in the <uicontrol>Quick Assist</uicontrol> menu:<ul
        id="ul_ckb_cfc_c4">
        <li>actions available on a selection made inside an attribute that contains an XPath
            expression:<ul id="ul_eys_hfc_c4">
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract template</uicontrol> - <ph
                  conref="xslt-refactoring-actions.dita#xslt-refactoring-actions/extract_template_short_desc"
                />
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Move to another stylesheet</uicontrol> - <ph
                  conref="xslt-refactoring-actions.dita#xslt-refactoring-actions/move_to_another_stylesheet_short_desc"
                />
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract local variable</uicontrol> - <ph
                  conref="xslt-refactoring-actions.dita#xslt-refactoring-actions/extract_local_var_sh_desc"
                />
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract global variable</uicontrol> - 
              <ph
                  conref="xslt-refactoring-actions.dita#xslt-refactoring-actions/extract_global_var_sh_desc"
                />
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract template parameter</uicontrol> - <ph
                  conref="xslt-refactoring-actions.dita#xslt-refactoring-actions/extract_templ_param_sh_desc"
                />
            </li>
            <li>
              <uicontrol>Extract global parameter</uicontrol> - <ph
                  conref="xslt-refactoring-actions.dita#xslt-refactoring-actions/extract_global_param_sh_desc"
                />
            </li>
          </ul><fig id="fig_pmp_k3c_c4">
            <title>XSLT Quick Assist Support - Refactoring Actions</title>
            <image href="../img/xslt_quick_assist_refactoring_actions.png" id="image_jpc_43c_c4"
              product="developer editor"/>
            <image href="../img/ec_xslt_quick_assist_refactoring_actions.png" id="image_nqc_yjc_c4"
              product="developerEclipse editorEclipse"/>
          </fig></li>
        <li>actions available when the cursor is positioned over the name of a component:<dl
            conref="xml-schema-quick-assist.dita#xml-schema-quick-assist/quick_assist_actions_list"
            id="ul_hpt_hhc_c4">
        <dlentry>
          <dt></dt>
          <dd></dd>
        </dlentry>
        </dl></li>
      </ul></p>
